{"tid":1233161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"班廢中廢老真係無批判性思考","createTime":"2019-06-16T17:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T17:42:01.000Z","uid":217869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e23c69d1d05294ba84b522b3ca1134c442f25917","tid":1233161,"uid":217869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:40:19.000Z","msg":"頭先係元朗X記食宵夜個陣，隔離檯兩公婆係度講<br />\n<br />\n位烈士單新聞。<br />\n<br />\n廢老男：岩岩收到風死左個𡃁仔同鄺宇俊傾唔掂數先去<br />\n<br />\n               跳樓，都唔知收左佢幾多錢先跳。呢次鄺宇俊<br />\n<br />\n               大獲喇，差佬有排查佢。咁後生死左就真係可<br />\n      <br />\n               惜。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽到呢度真係忍唔住問佢，你覺得人命值幾錢？<br />\n<br />\n點解到今時今日仲有人認為612企最前面食子彈食摧淚彈<br />\n<br />\n班學生，什至係黃衣烈士係收左錢呢？<br />\n<br />\n你問撫心自問邊有人會收錢冒着生命危險，犧牲性命去<br />\n<br />\n捍衛香港人自由？<br />\n<br />\n最後真係好多謝612企前排同比人拉左既烈士<br />\n<br />\n亦希望廢老廢中有返多少少批判性思考，唔好撚再睇<br />\n<br />\n埋d垃圾假新聞。<br />\n<br />\n屌真係好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07177efaaf0108fac90fd895ef5872004b61e7d3","tid":1233161,"uid":64131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:42:01.000Z","msg":"咩人就諗咩野"}]}